[[File:DjerbaMap.jpg|thumb|250px|Map of Djerba]]
'''Djerba''' ([[Wikipedia:Arabic|Arabic]]: جربة) is with its 514 km² the largest island off [[Wikipedia:North Africa|North Africa]], located in the [[Wikipedia:Gulf of Gabes|Gulf of Gabes]] off the coast of [[Tunisia]]. [[Sidi Jemour]] and [[Ajim]] in west Djerba were filmed in April 1976 for [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']].

The Tatooine beast of burden [[Jerba/Legends|Jerba]] took its name from that of the island.

